title: An Awe-Filled Christmas - Wonder, Worship and Waking Up
description: What if we could live each day with an ongoing sense of awe and appreciation? How would we change? Who would we become? Join us this Christmas for a series that examines how cultivating a sense of awe can change our perceptions and enlarge our souls all year long.

Whether we love the thought of taking a long trip, or wish we could just arrive at our destination, there is something to be learned from the Road Trip found in Joshua 3.

description: Doomsday. Judgment Day. Apocalypse. For millennia, people have feared the end of the world. This Good Friday and Easter we will be exploring  how Jesus of Nazareth fulfills this prophecy and offers us hope and healing for our deepest wounds.
